             was indicted for the <rs id="t18080113-31-off178" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18080113-31-off178" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18080113-31-off178" type="offenceSubcategory" value="murder"></interp>
               wilful murder of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18080113-31-victim308" type="victimName">
                           Joseph 
                           Walker
                        <interp inst="t18080113-31-victim308" type="surname" value="Walker"></interp>
