                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080113-31-defend306 t18080113-31-punish180"></join>
               Confined Three Month in Newgate
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18080113-31-punish181" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18080113-31-punish181" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18080113-31-punish181" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080113-31-defend306 t18080113-31-punish181"></join>
               fined One Shilling
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex jury, before the Lord Chief Baron.</p>
